\begin{align*} \int_{-\infty}^xf(t)~dt&=\int_{-\infty}^10~dt+\int_1^x\frac12(t-1)~dt\\\\ &=0+\frac12\left[\frac12(t-1)^2\right]_1^x\\\\ &=\frac14(x-1)^2\;, \end{align*}
